WEBVTT

00:03:29.863 --> 00:03:32.998
and just showed my male side.

00:03:32.998 --> 00:03:36.016
And each of them
had a different take on this.

00:03:36.016 --> 00:03:40.497
Bina said, "I love your soul,

00:03:40.497 --> 00:03:44.073
and whether the outside
is Martin and Martine,

00:03:44.073 --> 00:03:46.488
it doesn't it matter to me,
I love your soul."

00:03:46.488 --> 00:03:54.150
My son said, "If you become a woman,
will you still be my father?"

00:03:54.150 --> 00:03:57.377
And I said, "Yes,
I'll always be your father,"

00:03:57.377 --> 00:04:00.675
and I'm still his father today.